NUMERIC INPUT HEATING_MODE, SA_TEMP
NUMERIC OUTPUT ALARM_HEATING
NUMERIC TMR
Function SECTIMER

GOTO WATCHING

WATCHING:
IF SECTIMER((( HEATING_MODE = 1) and (SA_TEMP < 80)),1800,TMR) THEN 

ALARM_HEATING = 1  GOTO WAIT_LOOP

ELSE  IF (HEATING_MODE = 1) and (SA_TEMP > 80) then ALARM_HEATING = 0 

ENDIF   

WAIT_LOOP:
if TS > 10 THEN GOTO WATCHING


